|s 1           |              |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|soil particle-|13.2          |3.3           |5.9           |4.5           | 
|s 2           |              |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|soil particle-|13.7          |3.9           |6.9           |6.9           | 
|s 3           |              |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
