|Useful life (year-|10-15             |20                |30                | 
|s)                |                  |                  |                  | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Total capacity (M-|&lt;50            |200-1,000         |10,000-50,000     | 
|W)                |                  |                  |                  | 
